%description
Simply text adventures/visual novels engine and game.

It was designed to interpret games that are the mix of visual novels,
text quests and classical 90'ss quests.

%prep
%setup -q
%patch0 -p1

%build
%setup_compile_flags
echo 2 | ./configure.sh
%make PREFIX=/usr

%install
%makeinstall_std PREFIX=/usr

%files
%doc doc/*
